branchCategory.description:
&lt;p&gt;
The VXED2 is a pilot operated 2 port solenoid valve for a wide range of fluids. It features a built in power saving circuit that reduces power consumption during holding by 1/3. Available port size ranges 1/4 to 1 inch. Flow rate ranges from Cv of 2.0 to 9.5
&lt;/p&gt;

branchCategory.bullets:
&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt; Power saving circuit to reduce power consumption by 1/3 during holding operation &lt;/LI&gt;
&lt;LI&gt;Body material: brass (C37), stainless steel, CAC407&lt;/LI&gt;
&lt;LI&gt;Seal material available: NBR, FKM, EPDM&lt;/LI&gt;
&lt;LI&gt;Rated voltage: 24VDC, 12VDC&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;

